{"data": [{"id": "4742836", "title": "Kayne Anderson: Defensive BDC Overlooked By The Market", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A US Dollar symbol made of wood with leaves growing from it.\" data-id=\"1455774438\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Kayne Anderson BDC (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KBDC\" title=\"Kayne Anderson BDC, Inc.\">KBDC</a></span>) is a newcomer to the stock market, having started trading in Q2 2024. <a href=\"https://s204.q4cdn.com/976242841/files/doc_financials/2024/q3/KBDC_3Q-24_Investor-Presentation_2024-11-14_vFINAL.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">As of September 30, 2024</a>, its portfolio value amounted to $1.94B. KBDC concentrates on middle-market businesses, generating between $10m and $50m in EBITDA</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1455774438/image_1455774438.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742836-kayne-anderson-defensive-bdc-overlooked-by-the-market", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 09:11:55"}, {"id": "4742834", "title": "ASML: One Of The Strongest Buys Due To Its Huge Monopoly", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Electronics worker holding silicon wafer by cutting machine in clean room\" data-id=\"556415443\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5242px\" height=\"3932px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Monty Rakusen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>ASML Holdings N.V. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ASML\" title=\"ASML Holding N.V.\">ASML</a></span>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ASMLF\" title=\"ASML Holding N.V.\">OTCPK:ASMLF</a>) is a Dutch headquartered manufacturer of advanced photolithography machines, which are extremely essential for semiconductor chip production. I've followed the company for a long time and always understood how important it</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/556415443/image_556415443.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742834-asml-stock-one-of-strongest-buys-due-to-huge-monopoly", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 09:04:28"}, {"id": "4742832", "title": "Hensoldt Is An Attractive High Growth European Defense Stock To Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1635913482/image_1635913482.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"NATO Military aid to Ukraine army. Powerful German-made modern battle tank.\" data-id=\"1635913482\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"930px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1635913482/image_1635913482.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1635913482/image_1635913482.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1635913482/image_1635913482.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1635913482/image_1635913482.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1635913482/image_1635913482.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1635913482/image_1635913482.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1635913482/image_1635913482.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1635913482/image_1635913482.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">quantic69</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In September, I covered Hensoldt (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HAGHY\" title=\"Hensoldt AG\">OTCPK:HAGHY</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HNSDF\" title=\"Hensoldt AG\">OTCPK:HNSDF</a>) and reiterated my buy rating and that has worked out rather well with a 15.8% return compared to 10.5% for the S&amp;P 500. This brings the year-to-date return to 48.4% compared to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1635913482/image_1635913482.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742832-hensoldt-attractive-high-growth-european-defense-stock-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 08:56:15"}, {"id": "4742831", "title": "Drilling Tools International Slows Down While Relative Valuation Gets Expensive (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1210680753/image_1210680753.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Female Oil Worker at oil field with folder\" data-id=\"1210680753\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1210680753/image_1210680753.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1210680753/image_1210680753.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1210680753/image_1210680753.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1210680753/image_1210680753.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1210680753/image_1210680753.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1210680753/image_1210680753.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1210680753/image_1210680753.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1210680753/image_1210680753.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">chinaface</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>DTI Remains On The Balance</strong></h2> <p>I discussed Drilling Tools International (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DTI\" title=\"Drilling Tools International Corporation\">DTI</a></span>) in the past, and you can read the previous article <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4721079-drilling-tools-international-improving-drivers-and-relative-undervaluation-are-a-catch\">here</a>, published on September 14, 2024. In recent times, DTI strengthened its presence in wellbore optimization and downhole</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1210680753/image_1210680753.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742831-drilling-tools-international-slows-down-while-relative-valuation-gets-expensive-rating-dwongrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 08:50:45"}, {"id": "4742839", "title": "Thematic Investing: Tomorrow's Themes, Today", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482626443/image_1482626443.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"investing Stock Focusing thematic analysis investing\" data-id=\"1482626443\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482626443/image_1482626443.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482626443/image_1482626443.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482626443/image_1482626443.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482626443/image_1482626443.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482626443/image_1482626443.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482626443/image_1482626443.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482626443/image_1482626443.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482626443/image_1482626443.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">primeimages/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Linus Franngard &amp; Scott Gladstone</em></p> <h2>The case for thematic investing</h2> <p>Thematic investing has grown in prominence as a way for investors to align portfolios with the evolving trends shaping the future economy. Over the last</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1482626443/image_1482626443.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742839-thematic-investing-tomorrows-themes-today", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 08:45:00"}, {"id": "4742764", "title": "Employment Report: 227K Jobs Added In November, Above Expectations", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1132115640/image_1132115640.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businesswoman sharing ideas with colleague in meeting\" data-id=\"1132115640\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1132115640/image_1132115640.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1132115640/image_1132115640.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1132115640/image_1132115640.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1132115640/image_1132115640.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1132115640/image_1132115640.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1132115640/image_1132115640.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1132115640/image_1132115640.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1132115640/image_1132115640.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Luis Alvarez</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The latest employment report showed 227,000 jobs were added in November, above forecasts of the expected addition of 202,000 new jobs. Meanwhile, the unemployment rate ticked up to 4.2%.</p> <p>Here is an excerpt from the <a href=\"http://www.bls.gov/news.release/empsit.nr0.htm\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer noopener\">Employment Situation Summary</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1132115640/image_1132115640.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742764-employment-report-227k-jobs-added-november-above-expectations", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 08:30:00"}, {"id": "4742828", "title": "VTWO: The Diversified U.S. Stock ETF To Own In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1356518647/image_1356518647.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Financial term Small Capitalization Stocks on green finance background from graphs, charts. 3D render\" data-id=\"1356518647\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1356518647/image_1356518647.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1356518647/image_1356518647.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1356518647/image_1356518647.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1356518647/image_1356518647.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1356518647/image_1356518647.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1356518647/image_1356518647.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1356518647/image_1356518647.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1356518647/image_1356518647.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Vladimir Zakharov</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>The Vanguard Russell 2000 Index Fund ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VTWO\" title=\"Vanguard Russell 2000 Index Fund ETF Shares\">VTWO</a></span>) has underperformed the SPDR S&amp;P 500 ETF Trust (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPY\" title=\"SPDR\u00ae S&amp;P 500 ETF Trust\">SPY</a>) so far in 2024, delivering a ~20% gain against the ~29% total return for the S&amp;P 500 tracking ETF:</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1356518647/image_1356518647.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742828-vtwo-the-diversified-us-stock-etf-to-own-in-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 08:10:58"}, {"id": "4742827", "title": "UnitedHealth Group Still Fairly Valued After Recent News", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159946636/image_2159946636.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"UnitedHealthcare headquarters in Minnetonka, Minnesota, USA\" data-id=\"2159946636\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159946636/image_2159946636.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159946636/image_2159946636.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159946636/image_2159946636.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159946636/image_2159946636.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159946636/image_2159946636.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159946636/image_2159946636.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480